      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "Dockerfile are not useful for development time. You want to have everything installed locally as is already documented.\r\n\r\nThat said, the argument that Dockerfile do not belong here is in my opinion deeply flawed.\r\n\r\nRight now there is tons of documentation pages explaining how to compile bitcoin in different environments.\r\nSuch documentation can be replaced by dockerfile and tested as part of CI. \r\nThis is less maintenance rather than more and better notify us when there is something breaking in some distro.",
